Thou maist well goe and put it on, thou vnmannerly knight, vnworthie of a knights name (said the Spaniar
                     •
                  ) and hereupon I defie thée forthwith, that thou maist help thy Unckle, in whom thou puttest too great trust: & with a gallant and souereigne iesture, he presently shut down his visor.
